> **Strategic Takeaway:** The teams that wait for revenue data are the ones that learn about churn after it happens. The teams that watch support data are the ones that see it coming. Track escalation frequency. Track resolution time trends. Track ticket volume spikes. Track sentiment. The churn is predictable.

